WEBVTT

00:05:27.833 --> 00:05:33.323
or when the cult falls apart
due to external pressure or scandals.

00:05:33.323 --> 00:05:35.953
Many cults may be hard to identify,

00:05:35.953 --> 00:05:39.394
and for some, their beliefs,
no matter how strange,

00:05:39.394 --> 00:05:42.283
are protected under religious freedom.

00:05:42.283 --> 00:05:44.516
But when their practices 
involve harassment,

00:05:44.516 --> 00:05:45.390
threats,

00:05:45.390 --> 00:05:46.733
illegal activities,

00:05:46.733 --> 00:05:47.994
or abuse,

00:05:47.994 --> 00:05:50.713
the law can intervene.

00:05:50.713 --> 00:05:55.532
Believing in something should not come
at the cost of your family and friends,

00:05:55.532 --> 00:05:58.363
and if someone tells you to sacrifice
your relationships

00:05:58.363 --> 00:06:01.176
or morality for the greater good,